Description of the raygay fileformat

*** PATHS ***

circle <path-name> center radius normal
spiral <path-name> <path-name> radius windings offset

*** OBJECTS ***

extrusion <material-name> <path-name> radius segments pieces
box <material-name> <vector1> <vector2>
necklace <material-name> <path-name> num radius 
cylinder <material-name> radius <from-point> <to-point>
sphere <material-name> radius <center-point>

*** TRANSFORMATIONS ***

rotate <axis-vector> angle
translate <vector>
